18:28.170 --> 18:29.656
Yeah, well,
I didn't know you were you.

18:29.657 --> 18:31.168
And I didn't know
you weren't my aunt.

18:31.169 --> 18:31.699
Okay, all right,

18:31.700 --> 18:33.575
let's just call this a draw.

18:33.650 --> 18:35.723
Britta doesn't need to
ever know about this.

18:35.724 --> 18:38.720
Okay, I'd be happy to,
for a price.

18:40.634 --> 18:42.223
That was brave of you.

18:42.906 --> 18:44.865
I owe you an apology.

18:45.250 --> 18:47.103
It was rude to call you crazy.

18:47.587 --> 18:49.607
Maybe I haven't been
giving you enough credit.

18:50.452 --> 18:53.154
Oh, that's really sweet.
Tell you what.

18:53.155 --> 18:56.616
Why don't I go get Chang?
You can tell him that yourself.

18:59.451 --> 19:01.476
- Oh, no.
- My God, that was amazing!

19:01.624 --> 19:03.193
- Wow!
- Good job!

19:03.194 --> 19:05.159
- Thanks!
- Amazing!

19:05.251 --> 19:07.092
Way to go, man,
go! That was awesome.

19:07.093 --> 19:08.930
They beat the crap out of you.

19:09.894 --> 19:10.908
It's okay.
I did a lot of ad-libbing.

19:10.909 --> 19:14.070
Guys, I'm so sorry.

19:14.071 --> 19:16.426
Thank you so much.
That was amazing.

19:16.615 --> 19:17.777
Even I learned something.

19:17.778 --> 19:20.165
- Oh, Annie.
- We did it.

19:20.166 --> 19:22.532
- Group hug, group hug.
- Hug, hug.

19:22.537 --> 19:24.573
- Way to save the day.
- Nice work.

19:25.857 --> 19:28.243
Did you get hit in the
face with a baseball?

19:28.244 --> 19:28.906
Yep.

19:28.907 --> 19:30.457
Annie, before you say anything,

19:30.458 --> 19:31.912
I just want you to know,

19:32.028 --> 19:33.402
even though I did nothing wrong,

19:33.403 --> 19:34.308
I'm still gonna give you money.

19:34.309 --> 19:36.663
No. I can't take
your money, Pierce.

19:36.664 --> 19:38.572
I can't go from
depending on my parents

19:38.573 --> 19:39.878
to depending on you,

19:39.879 --> 19:42.447
which is why I'm gonna get a job.

19:42.448 --> 19:44.254
So you're cutting me off?

19:44.387 --> 19:45.195
No.

19:45.196 --> 19:48.148
Pierce, I know you
don't depend on anyone,

19:48.149 --> 19:50.650
but you do depend on
people depending on you,

19:51.122 --> 19:52.613
so I'm not gonna take your money.

19:53.162 --> 19:54.337
We're still friends?

19:54.338 --> 19:55.495
Give me a day.

19:56.393 --> 19:57.404
By the way,

19:57.616 --> 19:59.773
your mom was the
Period Fairy, right?

